Improved the ability of txt_mixin to replace one line before another.

This is used to change the figure placement options in a latex figure
after the latex has been generated by rst2latex.  The script searches
for the filename of the included graphic and then finds the
\\begin{figure} line directly above it.  \\begin{figure} can then be
replaced by \\begin{figure}[tb] or whatever.
